        <div class="reveal">
          <h4>Cards</h4>
          <div class="grid-2">
            <article class="card">
              <div class="card__eyebrow">Council member</div>
              <h3>Russell Jones</h3>
              <p class="card__meta">Ojibwe from Sagamok Anishnawbek &middot; Full-stack developer</p>
              <p class="body">Founder of OIATC. Began the work after a 2023 case-management contract at a First Nations Child and Family Advocacy Unit revealed the gap between systems sold and systems needed.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <div class="card__eyebrow">Council member</div>
