        <div class="sec__head reveal">
          <div><div class="sec__num">07 · Patterns</div></div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="sec__title">Section templates, composed from the kit.</h2>
            <p class="sec__intro">These are the only section templates oiatc.ca should need. Each composes existing components &mdash; no new primitives. A page that follows masthead &rarr; premise &rarr; pillars &rarr; candour &rarr; contact reads like a good short brief.</p>
