            <div class="mono" style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-3);">Headline</div>
            <div class="mono" style="font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink-2); margin-top: var(--gap-3);">Serif &middot; 300 &middot; Sentence case</div>
            <p class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px; margin-top: var(--gap-3); margin-bottom: 0;">One claim. As short as we can stand.</p>
