    {# 10 A11Y #}
    <section class="sec" id="a11y">
      <div class="shell">
        <div class="sec__head reveal">
          <div><div class="sec__num">10 · Accessibility</div></div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="sec__title">Plain sites are usually accessible sites &mdash; but we check.</h2>
            <p class="sec__intro">Targets below are minimums. Where we can exceed them without harming the design, we do.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal" style="border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);">
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Contrast &mdash; body text</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">AA+ &middot; &ge; 7:1 where possible</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Ink on Paper measures ~13:1 in light, ~14:1 in dark.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Contrast &mdash; secondary text</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">AA &middot; &ge; 4.5:1</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Ink-2 on Paper verified in both modes.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Contrast &mdash; UI (buttons, rules)</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">AA &middot; &ge; 3:1</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Rule-strong and button borders meet 3:1 against surfaces.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Focus ring</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">2px outline &middot; ember &middot; 2px offset</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Every focusable element. Never removed.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Reduced motion</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">Respect prefers-reduced-motion</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Reveal animations become instant; no transforms.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Hit targets</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">&ge; 44 &times; 44 px</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Buttons and nav links meet this at every density.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Language</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">lang attribute set</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Any Anishinaabemowin phrases receive their own lang attribute.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Skip link</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">Keyboard-first</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Skip to content is the first focusable element on every page.</span></div>
          <div class="a11y-row"><span style="font-size: 14px;">Landmarks</span><span class="mono" style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink);">header &middot; nav &middot; main &middot; footer</span><span class="body muted" style="font-size: 13px;">Every page exposes the same four landmarks in the same order.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
